    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been such a joy to own. This car is in really solid shape and has been well-loved and properly maintained. It runs like a dream and is ready for many more miles of adventures! It\u2019s the perfect blend of reliable and fun. I\u2019ve priced it to find a great new home quickly, so come check it out and take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love it!",
