    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera is a mechanically robust driver\u2019s car featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six powerplant equipped with VarioCam Plus. Power is delivered through a G96 6-speed manual transaxle, offering precise shift gates and optimal gear spacing. The IMS bearing has been proactively retrofitted, and the rear main seal is dry. The chassis retains its communicative feedback thanks to a well-sorted MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry. Performance is anchored by four-piston Brembo monoblock calipers over cross-drilled rotors, providing exceptional thermal management and bite. Finished in a classic palette, this 911 exhibits minor cosmetic patina consistent with spirited use but remains structurally sound and performance-ready.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
