    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. Meticulously maintained with a full service history, it offers a smooth, responsive drive that feels as reliable as the day it was bought. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a few minor stone chips reflect its honest road history. Inside, the leather upholstery is supple and clean, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s bolster consistent with careful use. All electronics, including the premium sound system and dual-zone climate control, function flawlessly. Recent updates include a fresh set of all-season tires and a complete fluid flush, ensuring it is ready for the road immediately. If you are looking for a dependable, high-quality ride that has been treated with genuine care, this is an excellent choice.",
      "price": 34500.0,
