    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This distinguished vehicle represents an exceptional opportunity for the discerning driver. Meticulously maintained and presenting in commendable condition, it offers a refined driving experience characterized by consistent mechanical performance and aesthetic poise. Every component has been evaluated to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for reliability and roadworthiness. A premier selection for those seeking a sophisticated balance of value and long-term excellence.",
      "price": 34900.0,
