    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking for a new home for my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been super dependable for all my errands and road trips. It looks great and runs even better\u2014perfect for someone who wants a reliable car without the brand-new price tag. I've taken good care of it, and I'm sure you'll love it just as much as I have. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 33800.0,
