      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies. This example retains its mechanical crispness with a factory 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a functional M-Variable differential lock. The chassis remains composed thanks to recent bushing refreshes and a documented subframe reinforcement, addressing the platform's primary structural concern. While the exterior shows honest signs of spirited use, the VANOS system has been professionally serviced, ensuring the high-revving valvetrain operates within factory tolerances. A true enthusiast\u2019s specimen that prioritizes drivetrain health and cornering dynamics.",
